reviews.review_text: This Day... Good Show.  Good Quality.  I'm especially grateful to be able to listen.  My ritual at work is; coffee>archive>Grateful Dead>Grateful Dead shows on this day>PLAY.  It's made the duldrums of clicking a dragging more interesting.  I know find myself noodling a bit during my work!  Hooray Archive!
